Project Overview

This project analyzes 3,000 Jumia customer orders to uncover insights into sales performance, 
customer behavior, and regional purchasing patterns. Using Power BI, 
I cleaned, modeled, and transformed the dataset into an interactive
ashboard supporting strategic e-commerce decision-making.

--  Key Insights

East & South regions generate the highest sales revenue.

Food & Beverages, Electronics, and Home Appliances lead in overall purchases.

Doctors and Students show the highest average spending.

Mid-income earners (â‚¦40Kâ€“â‚¦80K) make the highest number of purchases.

High-income customers make fewer but premium purchases.

Equal gender contribution to total revenue (Male 49.79% | Female 50.21%).

