--  Modeling Insights

The Star Schema enables a flexible and scalable structure,
allowing the dashboard to support filtering by region,
customer demographics, income brackets, and product segments.

This model makes it easy to answer business questions such as:

Which regions and categories drive the highest revenue?

How do income and occupation impact spending?

Which customer segments have the greatest growth potential?

-- Dashboard Insights

The dashboard visualizes:

Overall KPIs: Total Revenue, Average Revenue, Number of Orders, Total Income

Product & category performance

Country-level patterns

Gender contribution

Behavioral patterns (Income vs Quantity)

High-value customer segments

These visuals together reveal purchasing behaviors and segment-level profitability.

--  Recommendations

Target the East & South with region-specific promotions.

Create bundle offers for mid-income customers.

Offer premium product marketing for high-income and professional customers.

Maintain gender-neutral marketing due to equal contribution.

Promote top-performing categories through focused campaigns.

